x4freetext: High purity natural selenium (99.9999%, supplied by
Sigma-Aldrich, Germany) and high purity Al, Cu and
Ni foils (99.999%, supplied by Goodfellow, Metals,
England) were used. A thin layer of selenium was
prepared by vacuum deposition on Al-backing. The
thickness (~ 2 mu-m) was determined by weighing the
deposited selenium on the known area of Al-sheet
(50 mu-m thickness; 100 mm x100 mm area)
